'''玛丽·凯瑟琳·科尔文'''（英文：{{lang|en|Marie Catherine Colvin}}；{{bd|1956年|1月12日|2012年|2月22日|catIdx=Colvin}}），又譯'''瑪麗·卡彬'''，是著名的戰地記者，标志性特征是“独眼女侠”，生前三十多年一直在戰爭的前線報導新聞<ref name=Guardianobit />。她於2012年2月22日在[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]政府军[[霍姆斯大轰炸|炮击霍姆斯]]市时與法籍攝影記者{{tsl|en|Rémi Ochlik|雷米·歐赫利克}}被轟炸身亡<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1020/1/9/2/102019250.html |title=外國記者死亡　敘利亞：不知道這些記者入境 |publisher=[[中國評論通訊社|中國評論通訊社]] |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923224316/http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1020/1/9/2/102019250.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。身後火化，骨灰一半撒在長島外，一半撒在泰晤士河上。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年生活 ===
科尔文於1956年在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[紐約|紐約]][[皇后區|皇后區]][[阿斯托里亞_(皇后區)|阿斯托里亞]]出生，出生日期存疑<ref name="G obit">{{cite news|last=Greenslade|first=Roy|title=Marie Colvin obituary|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/feb/22/marie-colvin|newspaper=Guardian|date=February 22, 2012|accessdate=2012-02-23|archive-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130519052438/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/feb/22/marie-colvin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她1974年於出生地的高中[[牡蛎湾高校|牡蛎湾高校]]畢業，然後就讀[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]，並於1978年取得[[人類學|人類學]]學士學位資格畢業<ref name=nbcconnecticut>{{cite news |url=http://www.nbcconnecticut.com/news/local/Journalist-Killed-in-Syria-Attended-Yale--139988613.html |title=Journalist Killed in Syria Attended Yale |newspaper=NBC Connecticut |date=2012-02-22 |language=en |accessdate=2012-02-23 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060856/http://www.nbcconnecticut.com/news/local/Journalist-Killed-in-Syria-Attended-Yale--139988613.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=yaledailynews>{{cite news |url=http://www.yaledailynews.com/news/2012/feb/22/colvin-78-killed-while-covering-syrian-strike/?cross-campus |title=Colvin '78 killed in Syria |newspaper=Yale Daily News |date=2012-02-22 |language=en |accessdate=2012-02-23 |archive-date=2013-01-06 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130106065811/http://www.yaledailynews.com/news/2012/feb/22/colvin-78-killed-while-covering-syrian-strike/?cross-campus |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

父親威廉·J·科爾文 (William J. Colvin) 是二戰海軍陸戰隊退伍軍人，也是紐約市公立學校的英語教師，積極參與公民事務，曾擔任副縣長。她的母親 Rosemarie Marron Colvin 是長島公立學校的高中輔導員。她有兩個兄弟 ，以及兩個姐妹。

=== 職業生涯 ===
她畢業後的一年，於[[合众国际社|合众国际社]]位於纽约市的辦事處擔任记者，每天於午夜至凌晨六時工作，負責編採警方消息<ref name=ajr>{{cite news |title=Highway to the Danger Zone |first=Sherry |last=Ricchiardi |url=http://www.ajr.org/article.asp?id=746 |newspaper=[[American_Journalism_Review|American Journalism Review]] |date=2012-02-22 |language=en |access-date=2012-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223144924/http://www.ajr.org/article.asp?id=746 |archive-date=2012-02-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。1984年，科尔文升任合众社駐巴黎記者，並於1985年轉職英国《[[星期日泰晤士报|星期日泰晤士报]]》，在伦敦供职27年。科尔文早期並非專責擔任战地记者，她生命的轉折點發生在1986年，當時她擔任報館的駐中東特派員，並成為[[利比亞|利比亞]]被轟炸後首位訪問[[卡達菲|卡達菲]]的記者<ref>{{cite book |last=Miller |first= Judith |title=God has Ninety-Nine Names: Reporting from a Militant Middle East |url=https://archive.org/details/godhasninetynine00mill_0 |location=New York |publisher=Simon and Schuster |year=1997 |page=[https://archive.org/details/godhasninetynine00mill_0/page/232 232] |isbn=0684832283 }}</ref>。從1995年開始，科爾文轉任外交事務特派員，而其報導的新聞亦從過往專注於中東事務，擴展至[[車臣|車臣]]、[[科索沃|科索沃]]、[[塞拉利昂|塞拉利昂]]、[[津巴布韋|津巴布韋]]、[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]及[[東帝汶|東帝汶]]，成為英國戰地記者的精英部隊成員<ref name=ajr />。

1999年她在東帝汶採訪時，由於制止了親印尼武裝組織的一次行動，被指拯救了1500名婦女及兒童的生命。為保護這班平民，她選擇逗留在聯合國部隊駐紮地，並於該處向報館及電視報導新聞<ref name=Guardianobit>{{cite news|last=Greenslade|first=Roy|title=Marie Colvin obituary|trans_title=訃告：玛丽·科尔文 |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2012/feb/22/marie-colvin?newsfeed=true|newspaper=www.guardian.co.uk|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]] |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-23 |language=en }}</ref>，直至四日後這班平民獲救為止。

另外，由於她對車臣及科索沃的報導，令她獲得[[國際婦女媒體基金會|國際婦女媒體基金會]]的新聞勇氣獎<ref>{{cite news |title=Woman Journalist Gets Her Story: In Spite of Grenade Attack, Marie Colvin Files Her Report |first= |last= |url=http://www.antonnews.com/oysterbayenterprisepilot/2001/04/27/news/colvin.html |newspaper= |date=2001-04-27 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225055903/http://www.antonnews.com/oysterbayenterprisepilot/2001/04/27/news/colvin.html |archivedate=2012-02-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Veteran Sunday Times journalist Marie Colvin 'killed in heavy shelling in Syria' just hours after broadcast on ITN News At Ten |first=Charles |last=Walford |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2104711/Marie-Colvin-dead-Journalist-killed-Homs-Syria-hours-ITN-News-At-Ten-broadcast.html |newspaper=[[Mail_Online|Mail Online]] |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701233226/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2104711/Marie-Colvin-Sunday-Times-reporter-leave-Syria-day-died-says-mother.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Marie Colvin killed in Syria: life and times of distinguished war correspondent |first=Alex |last=Spillius |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9098180/Marie-Colvin-killed-in-Syria-life-and-times-of-distinguished-war-correspondent.html |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=en |archive-date=2018-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214140502/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9098180/Marie-Colvin-killed-in-Syria-life-and-times-of-distinguished-war-correspondent.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=mingpao />。科爾文亦有寫作和製作紀錄片，當中包括為BBC製作的《[[阿拉法特|阿拉法特]]：神話的背後》<ref>{{cite news |title=Death of Marie Colvin, American journalist of war |first=Nazish |last=Fatima |url=http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/11570335-death-of-marie-colvin-american-journalist-of-war |newspaper= |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=en |archive-date=2012-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224055010/http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/11570335-death-of-marie-colvin-american-journalist-of-war |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2005年一套講述處於戰爭地區的婦女的生存狀況的紀錄片《''[[:en:Bearing_Witness|Bearing Witness]]''》中，科爾文除了有在片中出現，還有參與當中的採訪任務<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120223/5950077.html |title=兩名西方記者在敘利亞被炸死 |publisher=北京新浪網 |date=2012-02-23 |accessdate=2012-02-24 |language=zh |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202224/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20120223/5950077.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科尔文的独眼形象成为新闻界一面招牌，其传奇事迹还被搬上荧幕。事發於2001年4月16日，當時玛丽·科尔文在斯里兰卡采访內戰。當時斯里蘭卡政府禁止外國傳媒進入被叛軍控制的北部泰米爾地區，而科爾文卻突破禁令，未經批准闖入禁區採訪，把當地不為人知的人道災難如實報導<ref name=mingpao>{{cite news |url=http://news.mingpao.com/20120223/taa2.htm |title=自問是否值得冒險 答案始終不變：值得 |language=zh-hant |date=2012-02-23 |accessdate=2012-02-23 |publisher=[[明報|明報]] |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912183600/https://news.mingpao.com/20120223/taa2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但在潛返中央政府管制區時，遭一名[[斯里兰卡政府军|斯里兰卡政府军]]士兵朝她發射榴彈炮襲擊，雖然當時她高舉記者證件<ref name=mingpao />，並多次呼叫「記者，記者！」，但仍然被政府軍炸伤，失去了左眼视力<ref name=guardian2001>{{cite news|last=Hodgson|first=Jessica|title=Sunday Times journalist may lose sight|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2001/apr/18/sundaytimes.pressandpublishing|newspaper=Guardian|date=2001-04-18|language=en|accessdate=2012-02-23|archive-date=2012-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225082042/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2001/apr/18/sundaytimes.pressandpublishing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=telegraph>{{cite news |title=Syria: Sunday Times journalist Marie Colvin 'killed in Homs' |first=Murray |last=Wardrop |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9097762/Syria-Sunday-Times-journalist-Marie-Colvin-killed-in-Homs.html |newspaper=[[每日電訊|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2012-02-22 |accessdate=2012-02-22 |language=en |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126210514/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9097762/Syria-Sunday-Times-journalist-Marie-Colvin-killed-in-Homs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Walt, Vivienne|url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2107394,00.html|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|title=Syria: War Reporter Marie Colvin and Photographer Rémi Ochlik Are Killed|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2012-02-22|language=en|archive-date=2012-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222173424/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2107394,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ausmcmay09"/>，並令左耳失聰<ref name=mingpao />。在被襲後，科爾文被拘留了10小時，其間沒接受任何治療，直至美國國務院施壓才放人<ref name=mingpao />，結果令她的傷殘變成永久，而事後科爾文亦患上[[创伤后心理压力紧张综合症|创伤后心理压力紧张综合症]]，需要住院治療。結果，在斯里蘭卡內戰的最後階段，科爾文成為了政府軍針對當地泰米爾人的[[戰爭罪行|戰爭罪行]]的目擊證人及中介<ref name="ausmcmay09">{{cite web|author=Colvin, Marie|title=Slain Tamil chiefs were promised safety|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/slain-tamil-chiefs-were-promised-safety/story-e6frg6t6-1225715467354|work=[[The_Australian|The Australian]]|date=May 25, 2009|accessdate=February 22, 2012}}</ref>。

2011年，當科爾文採訪[[2011年利比亚内战|利比亚内战]]之時，獲卡達菲邀約採訪，並可指明兩位同行的其他記者。自从战争开始的第一次国际采访起，她就一直与她的朋友，[[ABC_News|ABC News]]的[[克里斯汀·阿曼普|克里斯汀·阿曼普]]（Christiane Amanpour）<ref>{{cite news | url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/christiane-amanpour-interviews-libyas-moammar-gadhafi/story?id=13019942 | work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] | author=[[Christiane_Amanpour|Christiane Amanpour]] | title=Col Gaddafi 'brushed off the international pressure' | date=March 1, 2011 | accessdate=2012-02-23 | archive-date=2012-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224034336/http://abcnews.go.com/International/christiane-amanpour-interviews-libyas-moammar-gadhafi/story?id=13019942 | dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[BBC_News|BBC News]]的[[Jeremy_Bowen|Jeremy Bowen]]合作。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12607475 | work=BBC News | author=[[Jeremy_Bowen|Jeremy Bowen]] | title=Col Gaddafi 'brushed off the international pressure' | date=March 1, 2011 | accessdate=2012-02-23 | archive-date=2012-01-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123021349/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-12607475 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

科尔文曾经说过：“我并不是典型的战地记者，因为我注重的是战争中的人性，我想告诉人们战争究竟是个什么样子。几个世纪过去了，战争并未发生明显的变化。战场上依旧炮声隆隆，血肉横飞；战场外妻离子散；交战双方都不肯公开真相。所以，我的工作就是做一名战争证人。”

=== 死亡 ===
[[File:Bayeux_-_Mémorial_des_Reporters_5.JPG|thumbnail]]的記者紀念碑上]]
2012年2月，科爾文利用一輛[[越野摩托車|越野摩托車]]潛入敘利亞國境，以突破敘利亞政府為防止外國傳媒報導[[2011－2012年叙利亚反政府示威|反政府示威]]而實施的封鎖。進入敘利亞境內，科爾文逗留在[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]西部的[[巴巴艾瑪|巴巴艾瑪]]區內由[[自由叙利亚军|自由叙利亚军]]临时搭建<ref>{{cite news |url=http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2012-02/24/content_319615.htm?div=0 |title=叙军被指谋杀战地记者 |date=2012-02-24 |accessdate=2012-02-24 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[新京报|新京报]] |archive-date=2019-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717011251/http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2012-02/24/content_319615.htm?div=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的新聞中心，而2月21日晚，科爾文透過[[衛星電話|衛星電話]]分別向[[BBC|BBC]]、[[Channel4|Channel4]]、[[CNN|CNN]]及[[ITN_News|ITN News]]等新聞台報導當地現況<ref name=DMail2104711/>。

2月22日，霍姆斯的臨時新聞中心被敘利亞軍隊攻擊。科爾文與法國攝影記者[[雷米·歐赫利克|雷米·歐赫利克]]在逃離時，火箭擊中附近，造成此二人死亡。<ref name=telegraph /><ref>{{cite news |title='Foreign journalists killed' in Homs shelling |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/201222291445322238.html |newspaper=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |date=February 22, 2012 |accessdate=February 22, 2012 |archive-date=2012-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224181657/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/201222291445322238.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Veteran war reporter Marie Colvin killed in Syria |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/veteran-war-reporter-marie-colvin-killed-in-syria |publisher=[[Channel_4|Channel 4]] |date=February 22, 2012 |accessdate=February 22, 2012 |archive-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225042229/http://www.channel4.com/news/veteran-war-reporter-marie-colvin-killed-in-syria |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同業記者讓·皮埃爾·佩林（Jean-Pierre Perrin）與其它消息來源指出，敘利亞軍隊經由衛星電話訊號辨認出該臨時新聞中心，並蓄意攻擊該棟建築。<ref>{{cite news | title=Marie Colvin: Britain summons Syria ambassador over killing | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9098511/Marie-Colvin-Britain-summons-Syria-ambassador-over-killing.html | newspaper=[[The_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] | date=February 22, 2012 | accessdate=February 22, 2012 | archive-date=2012-02-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223183418/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9098511/Marie-Colvin-Britain-summons-Syria-ambassador-over-killing.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>敘利亞軍隊表示要殺掉「任何踏足敘利亞領土的記者」以阻止關於平民死亡的報導。2月22日晚上，霍姆斯的居民在街上哀悼科爾文與歐赫利克。<ref>{{Youtube|As1zOG6_2A4|حمص القصور مسائية 22-2-2012}}</ref>

== 私人生活 ==
科爾文曾兩度跟同為記者的帕特里克·畢曉普（Patrick Bishop）結婚，但兩次結婚的結局均是離婚收場。她亦曾嫁給另一位記者{{link-en|胡安·卡洛斯·古姆西奧|Juan Carlos Gumucio}}，但後來他於2002年自殺身亡<ref name="G obit"/>。科爾文生前住在[[西倫敦|西倫敦]]的[[哈默史密斯|哈默史密斯]]<ref name=DMail2104711>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2104711/Marie-Colvin-dead-Journalist-killed-Homs-Syria-hours-ITN-News-At-Ten-broadcast.html|title=Veteran American war reporter Marie Colvin killed when Syrian army shells media center just hours after her last TV broadcast|publisher=[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]]|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2012-02-22|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701233226/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2104711/Marie-Colvin-Sunday-Times-reporter-leave-Syria-day-died-says-mother.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

